{
  "stem": "17426.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And he just tore them off my shoulder and slid them across the rails.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The little box broke up, and all the instruments lay there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I looked at them, and I said, this is the end of me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Without these, I will never survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Nor will my father.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Beg your pardon.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "My father who was with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Yes, nor will my father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother was not with me, just my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I understood that my brother is on the same transport, also coming from the other camp to Auschwitz with the same transport.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a huge transport, perhaps as many as 100 cars.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we were asked to walk forwards and undress.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we undressed, and we came in front of a group of SS men.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One of them was obviously the reigning person, and he stood nonchalantly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we walked, five of us in front of him, naked as we were, taking in some air to show some chest, trying to look strong, rubbing our cheeks with our fists, so that they will look pink.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Trying to stretch out, so we wouldn't have such small behind.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he just mimicked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Some time he turned his eyes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Some time he turned his head.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Some time he just touched something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They knew what it meant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This was well-rehearsed and used many, many times.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they, according to his whim and to his decision, ordered people to the left or right.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it soon became evident that those that going to the left were elderly people, people that did not look like they would be the good group, so to speak, the strong ones.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then when it came to my father, they pointed him to the left and me to the right.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
